{"tid":1627670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲接受殺人 黃絲只能接受破壞","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:56:52.000Z","uid":223063,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54160546324adf9aea63d032b2b42e8b77d13522","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>真。香港人 加油</strong><br />\n請不要被一些連<strong>繁體字</strong>都不懂的人<br />\n反對我們自己香港人認為做對的事<br />\n當我們應有權利正在無理地被剝削<br />\n是否更加應該團結地爭取原有權利<br />\n並不是怪責一些為我們抗爭的少年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zXMPCc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzXMPCc9.jpg&h=62fc1bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CU7fxOn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCU7fxOn.jpg&h=85c7da53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港現在的前線警員由<strong>毅進制</strong>招募<br />\n政府是否有需要重新考慮這個制度<br />\n<strong>牠們</strong>的情緒管理或智力受世人質疑<br />\n給牠們過大的權力及槍械是否適當<br />\n當面對一定的壓力時能否保持專業<br />\n面對<strong>黑社會</strong>普通市民能否公平對待<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQDqUZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQDqUZ2.jpg&h=f9c3fe9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73TuCdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73TuCdo.jpg&h=ecd79a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEO2Xey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEO2Xey.jpg&h=f51d16fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SyJivzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSyJivzz.jpg&h=6132ea12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721元朗事件正正反映出警隊專業<br />\n警員看到市民被白毆打後轉身離去<br />\n並沒有任何上前去了解事件的意欲<br />\n更安排警員列隊及安排白衣人離去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GXphL6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXphL6X.jpg&h=b3704d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huOKq6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuOKq6X.jpg&h=381ce3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n831太子事件反映出警員不公執法<br />\n面對白衣人手持利器警員卻搭膊頭<br />\n一度聲稱現場不見可疑人士及武器<br />\n面對學生及市民卻無差別攻擊拘捕<br />\n警員不但沒有阻止手持武器的老人<br />\n卻攻擊正散去的市民放走犯罪人士<br />\n市民雙手舉高過頭及雙腳跪在地上<br />\n換來警員無理的最低武力胡椒噴霧<br />\n阻止救護人員搶救頭破血流的市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a2bQyN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a2bQyN.jpg&h=8eab9632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7r4q68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7r4q68.jpg&h=a8e4fef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n101荃灣事件反映出警員賊贓嫁禍<br />\n警員權力過大問題加劇了市民怨憤<br />\n全副武裝警員面對膠管浮水板市民<br />\n竟使用真槍並近距離射向男士左胸<br />\n警員沒有即時檢查男士傷口或急救<br />\n這是否警務人員應有的專業及素質<br />\n警務處一度放寬警員所擁有的權力<br />\n高官的子女卻身在外國勢力的地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mk9UOmB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmk9UOmB.jpg&h=aeefacea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dKeNoUX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdKeNoUX.jpg&h=30ae00a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上往往支持警隊不會是香港人<br />\n口裏說中立的人只不過是自私自利<br />\n當影響到他們日常生活便怪責自由<br />\n滿口道德觀念當玻璃破裂時便發茅<br />\n政府推行惡化及再三發展大象工程<br />\n他們亦沒有表達對此的不滿及訴求<br />\n到警察濫用權力導致市民頭破血流<br />\n還說活該及盲目支持警方濫用權力<br />\n願愛中國的人回去他們本屬的地方<br />\n請不要將香港變成你口中所說之地<br />\n希望更多市民了解不再黃藍的分別<br />\n現時的情況已演變為黑白良知之分<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XU9ChR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XU9ChR.jpg&h=27e96ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讓香港人成功爭取應有的權利訴求<br />\n在這日來到前請每一位要活着反抗<br />\n感謝每一位看到最後和理非陣間見<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革明<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由萬世都不朽<br />\n我願 榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n香港人反抗<br />\nStandwithHongKong"},{"pid":"5a25c53ac37416911276b41d3dbdd2b7d7e4787f","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09a7b03a2179905e935b93dcf581d1e0eaa9a3f","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2addcb3e6d52760b9df7a28ce77c64b189a2daa0","tid":1627670,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0039e3df002b3e2c04506a6f66c0390cb80ad2f","tid":1627670,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n聽日見！<br />\n香港人反抗啊"},{"pid":"ef184b488312166909ac0febd455e90235bc985c","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3029d8ee2050488d50ddce0e216e68c2c688def5","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"聽日要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126b5f5fb2a203527ecf38a2b0685b8fdab7b620","tid":1627670,"uid":13874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:27:50.000Z","msg":"［公投］就裝修目標公投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75246abc10f2c857db19eddb549cbc7a30a76107","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"126b5f5fb2a203527ecf38a2b0685b8fdab7b620","tid":1627670,"uid":13874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:27:50.000Z","msg":"［公投］就裝修目標公投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:35:32.000Z","msg":"已投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eff130e6674b6061ef140b98d6d22cb1d470487","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非"},{"pid":"a53c621cf1bcdf81cd8305ed9b14594dc7cf18a6","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />123456789"},{"pid":"a0964fc90e985c0461c5f022bed8059f45881caf","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禁止禁蒙面法"},{"pid":"60d73ca5baa98b551826549599e3c7fb992c7aa6","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b90dcd798e8ee68cad5d1135acb706338ab1e1","tid":1627670,"uid":223063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"出門口未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}